title: No Lp For My Last Ranked Solo/Duo Game
body:
So i won my last ranked game but after the game it wouldnt show my grade, end game chat or anything else so i restarded the client. When i came back i checked and i still had the win in my match history but i got no lp for the game. I would appreciate some help with this 

My account name is delmu720 (Eune)

replies.body: The [**EUNE Status Page**](http://status.leagueoflegends.com/#eune) mentions that we've noticed problems with LP values not showing up correctly. Looks like they're still working on a fix though.
Same thing just happened to me, I hope this gets resolved
